Short:    SmallEiffel mode for GoldEd 4
Uploader: Thomas Aglassinger <agi@sbox.tu-graz.ac.at>
Author:   Thomas Aglassinger <agi@sbox.tu-graz.ac.at>
Type:     text/edit
Kurz:     SmallEiffel Modus für GoldEd 4

TITLE

  GedEiffel

VERSION

  1.2

AUTHOR

  Thomas Aglassinger <agi@sbox.tu-graz.ac.at>

DESCRIPTION

  GedEiffel is a SmallEiffel mode for GoldEd. It consists of syntax
  parser, routine scanner, toolbar and a couple of ARexx scripts to
  interface `finder' and `pretty'.

FEATURES

  Colorful, practical and free.

NEW FEATURES

  Bugfixes and minor improvements.

SPECIAL REQUIREMENTS

  - GoldEd, version 4

  - SmallEiffel, available from aminet:dev/lang/

  - rexxdossupport.library, available from aminet:util/rexx/


AVAILABILITY

  aminet:text/edit/GedEiffel.lha

PRICE

  Freeware.

DISTRIBUTABILITY

  Freely distributable as long no files are added or removed from the
  archive.

